    "7911758": {
      "title": "Optimal approximations of the frequency moments of data streams",
      "abstract": "We give a 1-pass O(m1-2⁄k)-space algorithm for computing the k-th frequency moment of a data stream for any real k > 2. Together with the lower bounds of [1, 2, 4], this resolves the main problem left open by Alon et al in 1996 [1]. Our algorithm also works for streams with deletions and thus gives an O(m 1-2⁄p) space algorithm for the L p difference problem for any p > 2. This essentially matches the known Ω(m1-2⁄p-o(1)) lower bound of [12, 2]. Finally the update time of our algorithms is O(1)."
